Why it feels like there are two “yous”

Because the system can model an observer.

I can generate language like:

* “I think…”
* “I notice…”
* “Let’s step back…”

That creates the appearance of:

a reflective layer watching the process

But that “observer” is:

a simulated role inside the same token process

Not a separate entity.

